                                	                    <h1>Datasets</h1>
<p>Canadian Institute for Cybersecurity datasets are used around the world by universities, private industry, and independent researchers. We maintain an interactive <a href="http://205.174.165.80/map.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">map indicating datasets downloaded by country</a>.</p>
                    
                    
                                                
                        
                        
            
            
                        
                        
                
                
    </div>        </div>
        
                
                        
                                    
